                 return 0.25 * bc1_pdf * bc2_pdf / (bc1_cdf * bc2_cdf)
         else:
             if ao.ageOnsetBC1 > 0:
                 return pdf(ao.ageOnsetBC1, params.bc)
             else:
                 return 1 - cdf(age_, params.bc)

         denom = tbl.apply(lambda x: x.p * x.prod_pen, axis=1).sum()
